{"tid":1301841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[on9] 近百警員手持盾牌拆走大埔連儂牆部分紙條","createTime":"2019-07-09T17:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T18:00:07.000Z","uid":201558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a4f9518c673b81a88b4936653272f76c16bfd7eb","tid":1301841,"uid":201558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:49:03.000Z","msg":"【行動過程．有片】在大埔火車站連儂牆，張貼了早前在 7.7 清場期間，挑釁市民「隻揪」的警員資料。警方在凌晨採取行動，近百機動部隊警員和便衣探員手持盾牌，進入大埔火車外的隧道，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">拆走載有該名警員資料的紙條，整個行動歷時約 10 分鐘，</span></strong></span>之後警員離開，未有拆走連儂牆其他紙條。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2296184957133778?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F2296184957133778%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBFLn0p5rLcPQxw7X33U7JQw%3D&h=94c703e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/2296184957133778?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知班克警係咪又想驗指模啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04cd893ccac672ae0661dc081c0d1d1c92348a00","tid":1301841,"uid":228195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T17:54:57.000Z","msg":"應該難D<br />\n行過摸到又有指模<br />\n可能印刷鋪個阿姐又有指模<br />\n賣紙果個又有指模"},{"pid":"52d18240ac6784f2501deae5928d98f5a79d8a2b","tid":1301841,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T18:00:07.000Z","msg":"歡迎入嚟一齊討論啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「長文慎入」勇武又好、和理非又好，自己香港自己救！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1299934/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1299934/page/1</a>"}]}